  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7455e1b1af245b34c95fc9187c26d9ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: CastleWarnerIntroDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  npcName: Weary Courier
  npcSprite: {fileID: 0}
  dialogue:
  - You there... you look like someone with a death wish. Perfect.
  - I was supposed to deliver this last red packet to the king, but I am not going
    anywhere near that castle.
  - The king is furious. The deliveries are late and he has been taking it out on
    everyone.
  - The guards look ready to attack, and the castle door is sealed with some kind
    of cipher lock. No one has been able to crack it.
  - Going in there is a suicide mission. But someone has to do it.
  - "Here, take this packet. Deliver it to the king if you can. May fortune favour
    you."
